# Pipeline: streaming
# Category: TV & Movie Streaming
# 10 apps — streaming platforms, watchlists, and discovery tools
# Generated: 2026-04-06

name: FlixVault Cinema
prefix: FVC
type: Movie Streaming Platform
category: Streaming Video
description: Netflix-style movie streaming with HLS adaptive bitrate via Video.js. Stripe subscription tiers (Free/Standard/4K). TMDb API integration for metadata, poster art, and cast info. Includes continue-watching, multiple profiles, and parental controls.
features: HLS adaptive streaming, Stripe subscription tiers, TMDb metadata sync, multi-profile support, continue-watching queue, parental content locks
design_bg: #0A0A0A
design_primary: #E50914
design_vibe: Dark cinematic red
budget: 750

name: BingeRadar Discovery
prefix: BGD
type: Show Discovery Engine
category: Streaming Discovery
description: AI-powered TV show and movie recommendation engine using collaborative filtering and OpenAI embeddings. Cross-platform watchlist aggregation from Netflix, Hulu, Prime via JustWatch API. Includes mood-based filters, "surprise me" roulette, and taste-match scores.
features: AI recommendation engine, JustWatch API aggregation, mood-based filters, surprise-me roulette, taste-match percentage, cross-platform search
design_bg: #1A1A2E
design_primary: #E94560
design_vibe: Dark discovery neon pink
budget: 650

name: SeriesSync Tracker
prefix: SST
type: Episode Tracker
category: Streaming Productivity
description: Trakt.tv-style episode tracking with automatic progress sync via Plex and Jellyfin webhooks. Calendar integration via Google Calendar API for upcoming episodes. Push notifications via OneSignal when new episodes air. Community ratings and spoiler-free discussion boards.
features: Plex/Jellyfin webhook sync, episode air-date calendar, OneSignal push alerts, spoiler-free forums, seasonal binge planner, watch history export
design_bg: #16213E
design_primary: #0F3460
design_vibe: Deep navy organized
budget: 600

name: CritiqHub Reviews
prefix: CHR
type: Review Aggregator
category: Streaming Social
description: Letterboxd-meets-Rotten-Tomatoes review platform for movies and TV shows. User reviews with spoiler tags, critic vs audience scores, and half-star ratings. OAuth via Google and Apple. Share watchlists as curated lists with custom cover art and OG meta previews.
features: critic vs audience dual scores, spoiler-tag system, curated shareable lists, OAuth Google/Apple login, OG meta social previews, half-star granular ratings
design_bg: #F5F5F5
design_primary: #FFB400
design_vibe: Clean review gold light
budget: 600

name: WatchPartyGo Live
prefix: WPG
type: Synchronized Watch Party
category: Streaming Social
description: Teleparty-style synchronized viewing rooms with WebSocket-based playback sync. Video chat overlay via Daily.co WebRTC. Supports YouTube, Twitch embed, and self-hosted HLS streams. Emoji reactions, live polls, and integrated group chat with GIF support via Giphy API.
features: WebSocket playback sync, Daily.co video chat overlay, YouTube/Twitch embed, Giphy-powered chat, live polls during playback, emoji reaction stream
design_bg: #1B0536
design_primary: #9B59B6
design_vibe: Dark party purple
budget: 700

name: SubDub Localize
prefix: SDL
type: Subtitle & Dubbing Platform
category: Streaming Tools
description: OpenSubtitles API-powered subtitle search and editor with in-browser timing sync. AI auto-translate via DeepL API for 30+ languages. Community subtitle upload and voting. SRT/VTT/ASS format conversion and style editor for font, color, and positioning.
features: OpenSubtitles API search, DeepL auto-translate, in-browser timing editor, SRT/VTT/ASS converter, community subtitle voting, custom style presets
design_bg: #212121
design_primary: #00BFA5
design_vibe: Dark subtitle teal
budget: 550

name: TrailerDrop Preview
prefix: TDP
type: Trailer & Preview Hub
category: Streaming Discovery
description: YouTube Data API-powered trailer aggregation with upcoming release calendars. TMDB and OMDB API for metadata enrichment. Personalized hype-score algorithm based on genre preferences and watch history. Countdown timers for theatrical and streaming release dates.
features: YouTube trailer aggregation, TMDB/OMDB metadata, personalized hype-score, release countdown timers, genre preference engine, watchlist-to-calendar sync
design_bg: #0D0D0D
design_primary: #FF6F00
design_vibe: Dark trailer orange
budget: 500

name: CinemaLedger Catalog
prefix: CLC
type: Personal Media Library
category: Streaming Productivity
description: Plex-style personal media catalog for physical and digital collections. Barcode scanning via QuaggaJS for Blu-ray and DVD lookup against OMDB. Lending tracker, insurance valuations, and shelf-location organizer. Export collection to CSV and Notion via API.
features: QuaggaJS barcode scanner, OMDB disc lookup, lending tracker with reminders, insurance valuation calculator, Notion export integration, shelf-location map
design_bg: #FAFAFA
design_primary: #37474F
design_vibe: Clean catalog slate light
budget: 500

name: SceneCut Clips
prefix: SCC
type: Video Clip & Meme Creator
category: Streaming Social
description: FFmpeg-powered in-browser video clipper for creating shareable GIFs and short clips from movie scenes. Cloudinary for CDN hosting and image transforms. Watermark overlays, caption generators with meme-style fonts, and direct share to Twitter/Reddit via OAuth.
features: FFmpeg in-browser clipping, Cloudinary CDN hosting, meme caption generator, watermark overlay, Twitter/Reddit direct share, GIF/MP4/WebM export
design_bg: #18181B
design_primary: #F43F5E
design_vibe: Dark creator rose
budget: 600

name: NightOwl Schedule
prefix: NOS
type: Streaming TV Schedule
category: Streaming Tools
description: TV Maze API-powered live TV and streaming schedule aggregator. Personalized prime-time planner that organizes tonight's shows across all subscribed platforms. Slack and Discord bot integration for group viewing coordination. Time-zone-aware scheduling with DVR conflict detection.
features: TV Maze API schedule sync, multi-platform prime-time planner, Slack/Discord bot alerts, timezone-aware grid view, DVR conflict detector, weekly digest email
design_bg: #0F172A
design_primary: #6366F1
design_vibe: Dark schedule indigo
budget: 550
